biocViews: GeneticVariability
Package: SNVMutationTypes
Title: Extract SNV mutation types from VCF files
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Giulia", "Fois", email="giuliafois5@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package exports functions to get and count mutation
    types starting from  a VCF file. A mutation type defined as a UP[REF>ALT]DOWN string. The
    reference and alternative nucleotides are taken from the VCF, whereas the upstream and downstream 
    sequences from a reference genome indicated by the user.
Imports: Biostrings, GenomicRanges, tools, VariantAnnotation
Encoding: UTF-8
